{
  "video_id": "exb9s0KwDLM",
  "title": "Three reason to advocate basic income - Guy Standing at WEF, Davos 2017",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 390.0,
      "end_time": 3300.0,
      "text": "As work is changing...\nis a universal basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3300.0,
      "end_time": 6930.0,
      "text": "really a solution to this problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6930.0,
      "end_time": 11309.0,
      "text": "First, umm, Guy. Well thank you very much"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11309.0,
      "end_time": 13980.0,
      "text": "and welcome to everybody and thanks for"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13980.0,
      "end_time": 15809.0,
      "text": "coming to this session. When you've been"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15809.0,
      "end_time": 18119.0,
      "text": "working on a subject for 30 years and"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18119.0,
      "end_time": 19680.0,
      "text": "you're suddenly told you have four to"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 19680.0,
      "end_time": 22020.0,
      "text": "five minutes to give your perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22020.0,
      "end_time": 25500.0,
      "text": "you feel the slight sense of awe and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25500.0,
      "end_time": 28560.0,
      "text": "want to begin actually by a little poem"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28560.0,
      "end_time": 32309.0,
      "text": "from Barbara Wootton who said: it's from"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32308.999999999996,
      "end_time": 36000.0,
      "text": "the champions of the impossible rather"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36000.0,
      "end_time": 39030.0,
      "text": "than the slaves of the possible that"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39030.0,
      "end_time": 43290.0,
      "text": "evolution draws its creative force. And I"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43290.0,
      "end_time": 45829.0,
      "text": "use that in our 25th anniversary because"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 45829.0,
      "end_time": 48030.0,
      "text": "we've been going through a period where"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48030.0,
      "end_time": 49500.0,
      "text": "we've been doing a lot of fundamental"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49500.0,
      "end_time": 51050.0,
      "text": "research on the feasibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51050.0,
      "end_time": 54690.0,
      "text": "affordability,  implications of a basic"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54690.0,
      "end_time": 58140.0,
      "text": "income. And for many years totally"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 58140.0,
      "end_time": 61020.0,
      "text": "ignored; but in the last couple of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61020.0,
      "end_time": 63510.0,
      "text": "there has been suddenly been a huge surge of"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63510.0,
      "end_time": 68939.0,
      "text": "interest partly by a realization about"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68939.0,
      "end_time": 72119.0,
      "text": "automation. Now I want to stress that"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72119.0,
      "end_time": 75960.0,
      "text": "that is not my rationale for a basic"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75960.0,
      "end_time": 79290.0,
      "text": "income. It never has been. But it's quite"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79290.0,
      "end_time": 81000.0,
      "text": "useful because it's made us much more"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81000.0,
      "end_time": 85770.0,
      "text": "topical. The reason I felt that I always"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85770.0,
      "end_time": 88700.0,
      "text": "fought for a basic income is a threefold."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88700.0,
      "end_time": 93110.0,
      "text": "First, it's a means of social justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93110.0,
      "end_time": 96210.0,
      "text": "This goes back to Thomas Paine and Henry"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96210.0,
      "end_time": 99360.0,
      "text": "George and people who said public wealth"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99360.0,
      "end_time": 104250.0,
      "text": "is created over generations. And any of"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104250.0,
      "end_time": 107009.0,
      "text": "us know or should know and have the"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107009.0,
      "end_time": 110100.0,
      "text": "humility to know that our income and"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110100.0,
      "end_time": 112259.0,
      "text": "wealth is fundamentally due to the"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112259.0,
      "end_time": 114240.0,
      "text": "contributions of previous generations"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114240.0,
      "end_time": 115740.0,
      "text": "and much more than anything you and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115740.0,
      "end_time": 119520.0,
      "text": "do ourselves. And therefore if you allow"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119520.0,
      "end_time": 121920.0,
      "text": "private inheritance we should also have"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121920.0,
      "end_time": 124079.0,
      "text": "public inheritance as a social dividend"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124079.0,
      "end_time": 127350.0,
      "text": "on public wealth created. That means of"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127350.0,
      "end_time": 130860.0,
      "text": "social justice is fundamental behind why"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 130860.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131920.0,
      "text": "I believe in a basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131920.0,
      "end_time": 135040.0,
      "text": "The second reason is that it is a means"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135040.0,
      "end_time": 139959.0,
      "text": "to enhance republican freedom. Republican"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139959.0,
      "end_time": 142240.0,
      "text": "freedom is different from standard"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142240.0,
      "end_time": 144790.0,
      "text": "liberal forms of freedom in the sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144790.0,
      "end_time": 150430.0,
      "text": "that it means freedom from domination by"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 150430.0,
      "end_time": 153160.0,
      "text": "figures of authority using up their"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153160.0,
      "end_time": 156630.0,
      "text": "arbitrary power. It is a mechanism for"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156630.0,
      "end_time": 159700.0,
      "text": "enhancing republican freedom. And the"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159700.0,
      "end_time": 162850.0,
      "text": "third reason is that it is a means of"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162850.0,
      "end_time": 165489.0,
      "text": "providing people with basic security."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165489.0,
      "end_time": 169330.0,
      "text": "Basic security. And in that regard, we"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 169330.0,
      "end_time": 172720.0,
      "text": "claim that those of us who support basic"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 172720.0,
      "end_time": 173080.0,
      "text": "income"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 173080.0,
      "end_time": 176230.0,
      "text": "it is not for eradicating poverty per se,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176230.0,
      "end_time": 180450.0,
      "text": "it is for handling the issue of"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180450.0,
      "end_time": 183730.0,
      "text": "insecurity. I listened this morning to"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 183730.0,
      "end_time": 185650.0,
      "text": "the very illustrious panel"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 185650.0,
      "end_time": 188110.0,
      "text": "saying what should be done to help the"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 188110.0,
      "end_time": 190660.0,
      "text": "squeezed middle class. I listen very very"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 190660.0,
      "end_time": 194040.0,
      "text": "intently. I couldn't hear a single policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194040.0,
      "end_time": 197140.0,
      "text": "that was addressed to the precariat or"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 197140.0,
      "end_time": 199410.0,
      "text": "to the groups that are facing chronic"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 199410.0,
      "end_time": 202390.0,
      "text": "insecurity today. Because that is behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 202390.0,
      "end_time": 205720.0,
      "text": "this drifter populism. That is behind so"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 205720.0,
      "end_time": 207790.0,
      "text": "many of the mental health problems and"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 207790.0,
      "end_time": 211989.0,
      "text": "so on mental health is improved by basic"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 211989.0,
      "end_time": 216040.0,
      "text": "security. Mental development is improved"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216040.0,
      "end_time": 219549.0,
      "text": "by basic security. And what we've found"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 219549.0,
      "end_time": 222160.0,
      "text": "in our pilots - and we've done pilots - I"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222160.0,
      "end_time": 224320.0,
      "text": "wish people would look at the evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224320.0,
      "end_time": 226329.0,
      "text": "rather than continue with their views."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 226329.0,
      "end_time": 229660.0,
      "text": "But we've done pilots covering thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 229660.0,
      "end_time": 232989.0,
      "text": "of people. And most fundamentally we"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 232989.0,
      "end_time": 235810.0,
      "text": "found that the emancipatory value of"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 235810.0,
      "end_time": 237670.0,
      "text": "a basic income is greater than the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 237670.0,
      "end_time": 240220.0,
      "text": "value. And i can explain that at length,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 240220.0,
      "end_time": 243760.0,
      "text": "but the point is that it gives people a"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 243760.0,
      "end_time": 247630.0,
      "text": "sense of control of their time so that"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 247630.0,
      "end_time": 251470.0,
      "text": "the value of work grow relative to the"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 251470.0,
      "end_time": 254350.0,
      "text": "demands of labor; so that the values of"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 254350.0,
      "end_time": 256810.0,
      "text": "learning and public participation grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 256810.0,
      "end_time": 260229.0,
      "text": "rather than just so surviving; so that the"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 260228.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262960.0,
      "text": "values of citizenship are strengthened"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 262960.0,
      "end_time": 266440.0,
      "text": "the values of altruism and tolerance we"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 266440.0,
      "end_time": 268420.0,
      "text": "found the evidence from basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 268420.0,
      "end_time": 270790.0,
      "text": "experiments that show that these are"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 270790.0,
      "end_time": 275230.0,
      "text": "enhanced we know as individuals and"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275230.0,
      "end_time": 277950.0,
      "text": "groups that at the moment society is"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 277950.0,
      "end_time": 280990.0,
      "text": "suffering from a deprivation of those"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280990.0,
      "end_time": 283870.0,
      "text": "values of altruism and tolerance. So for"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 283870.0,
      "end_time": 286000.0,
      "text": "me I think a basic income is not a"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 286000.0,
      "end_time": 288660.0,
      "text": "panacea but it is part of the new"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 288660.0,
      "end_time": 290640.0,
      "text": "distribution system that we should be"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 290650.0,
      "end_time": 292860.0,
      "text": "building for the 21st century. Thank you"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 292870.0,
      "end_time": 293800.0,
      "text": "very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 293800.0,
      "end_time": 294300.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much"
    }
  ]
}